'''''Thousand Parsec'''''（'''''TP'''''）是[[自由软件|自由开源软件]]，一个空间[[回合制策略游戏|回合制策略游戏]][[框架|框架]]。''Thousand Parsec''常常被误认为一个游戏<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.thousandparsec.net/tp/gettingstarted.php#content| title=About Thousand Parsec| date=2008-03-17| access-date=2009-04-01| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090328201842/http://www.thousandparsec.net/tp/gettingstarted.php#content| archive-date=2009-03-28| dead-url=yes}}</ref>但它仅仅是一个创造游戏的平台，通常产生[[4X概念体系|4X概念体系]]的游戏,：eXplore, eXpand, eXploit和eXterminate。''Thousand Parsec''体现此特点的游戏包括[[Reach_for_the_Stars_(computer_game)|Reach for the Stars]]'', ''[[Stars!|Stars!]]'', ''[[VGA_Planets|VGA Planets]]'', ''[[Master_of_Orion|Master of Orion]]''和''[[Galactic_Civilizations|Galactic Civilizations]]''.
不像闭源商业产品，此项目能扎干玩家电脑的机能。有着极高的可定制能力。

== 历史 ==
Tim Ansell在2002年以另一个名字开始了这个项目<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.thousandparsec.net/tp/pipermail.php/tp-devel/2006-January/000154.html| title=Thousand Parsec goals and direction| date=2006-01-02| accessdate=2006-11-21| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070329001146/http://www.thousandparsec.net/tp/pipermail.php/tp-devel/2006-January/000154.html| archive-date=2007-03-29| dead-url=yes}}</ref>起初只是''[[Stars!|Stars!]]''克隆。不久，Tim d决定仿照"''[[Worldforge|Worldforge]]''模式"，不过是建立太空帝国类的游戏框架。

2006年，''Thousand Parsec''未达到预想目标。不光低估了工作的负担，而且没有吸引到任何新开发者。''Thousand Parsec''尽管遇到挫折，但是仍有巨大的代码资源，通过[[Ohloh|Ohloh]]项目状态显示，有95000行代码。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ohloh.net/projects/3679|title=Ohloh Project Stats, Thousand Parsec, Project Cost|accessdate=2007-05-27|archive-date=2007-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070501202825/http://www.ohloh.net/projects/3679|dead-url=no}}</ref>
2006年晚些时候，进度进展加快<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ohloh.net/projects/3679/analyses/latest|title=Ohloh Project Stats, Thousand Parsec, Code|accessdate=2007-05-27|archive-date=2007-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070928001358/http://www.ohloh.net/projects/3679/analyses/latest|dead-url=no}}</ref>不少新的成员加入。开始研发AI，因此有编程竞赛<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thousandparsec.net/tp/news.php/2007-01-16-1130|title=Thousand Parsec: News - Thousand Parsec AI Programming Competition!|date=2007-01-16|access-date=2009-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070928004844/http://www.thousandparsec.net/tp/news.php/2007-01-16-1130|archive-date=2007-09-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>活跃地在[[linux.conf.au|linux.conf.au]]进行宣传。

2007年，''Thousand Parsec''在[[Google_Summer_of_Code|Google Summer of Code]]中得到三个名额。<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.thousandparsec.net/tp/news.php/2007-04-14-1326| title=Thousand Parsec: News - Google Summer of Code Allocations| date=2007-04-14| accessdate=2007-05-11| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070928004832/http://www.thousandparsec.net/tp/news.php/2007-04-14-1326| archive-date=2007-09-28| dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2008年，''Thousand Parsec''幸运的得到8个[[Google_Summer_of_Code|Google Summer of Code]]位置。<ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.thousandparsec.net/tp/news.php/2008-04-23-1400| title=Thousand Parsec: News - Meet Thousand Parsec GSoC 2008 Students| date=2008-04-23| accessdate=2008-05-04| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080627161829/http://www.thousandparsec.net/tp/news.php/2008-04-23-1400| archive-date=2008-06-27| dead-url=yes}}</ref>新项目包括三个新的规则设定，一个三维客户端（基于[[Ogre|Ogre]]），三个AI相关项目，以及一个服务端扩展和单人游戏有关的项目。

